Brave	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Halfling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Advantage on saving throws you make to avoid or end the Frightened condition.	KEY:Halfling ~ Brave																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Halfling Nimbleness	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Halfling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You can move through the space of any creature that is a size larger than you, but you can't stop in the same space.	KEY:Halfling ~ Halfling Nimbleness																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Luck	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Halfling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you roll a 1 on the d2O of a D2O Test, you can reroll the die, and you must use the new roll.	KEY:Halfling ~ Lucky																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Naturally Stealthy	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Halfling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You can take the Hide action even when you are obscured only by a creature that is at least one size larger than you.	KEY:Halfling ~ Naturally Stealthy																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

