Adrenaline Rush	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Orc Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You can take the Dash action as a Bonus Action. When you do so, you gain a number of Temporary Hit Points equal to your Proficiency Bonus. You can use this trait a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Short or Long Rest.	KEY:Orc ~ Adrenaline Rush																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Darkvision	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Orc Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Darkvision with a range of 120 feet.	KEY:Orc ~ Darkvision									BONUS:VAR|DarkvisionRange|120|TYPE=Base						SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Relentless Endurance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Orc Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When you are reduced to 0 Hit Points but not killed outright, you can drop to 1 Hit Point instead. Once you use this trait, you can't do so again until you finish a Long Rest.	KEY:Orc ~ Relentless Endurance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

