Tiefling size	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Medium (about 4-7 feet tall) or Small (about 3-4 feet tall), chosen when you select this species	KEY:Tiefling ~ Tiefling Size									BONUS:VAR|POOL_Racial_Size|1																		SOURCEPAGE:PHB 
