Fire Resistance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Tiefling Trait	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have resistance to Fire damage.	KEY:Tiefling ~ Fire Resistance																											SOURCEPAGE:PHB

Abyssal	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Fiendish Legacy	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your fiendish legacy is Abyssal.	KEY:Fiendish Legacy ~ Abyssal						TEMPLATE:Fiendish Legacy ~ Abyssal	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Poison Spray	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Ray of Sickness|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Hold Person|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	ABILITY:Tiefling Trait|AUTOMATIC|Tiefling ~ Poison Resistance	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
Chtonic	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Fiendish Legacy	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your fiendish legacy is Chthonic.	KEY:Fiendish Legacy ~ Chthonic						TEMPLATE:Fiendish Legacy ~ Chthonic	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=ATWILL|CASTERLEVEL=1|Chill Touch	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|False Life|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=3	SPELLS:Tiefling Cantrip|TIMES=1|CASTERLEVEL=1|Ray of Enfeeblement|PRECLASS:1,TYPE.Base=5	ABILITY:Tiefling Trait|AUTOMATIC|Tiefling ~ Necrotic Resistance	SOURCEPAGE:PHB
